60|$|The way he sank on {{the table}} in exhaustion, {{drinking}} his milk, his will, nevertheless, so perfect and unblemished, triumphant, though his body was broken and in anguish, was almost <b>too</b> <b>much</b> <b>to</b> <b>bear.</b> My heart was wrung for my countryman, wrung till it bled.|$|E
