60|$|She {{looked at}} him silently, still with the blank despair on her face; but then the tears began to fill her blue eyes, and her lip trembled. The strong man had had <b>too</b> <b>much</b> <b>to</b> <b>bear</b> that day. He let his head fall beside hers and sobbed.|$|E
